name: orientdb
description:
OrientDB is an Open Source Multi-Model NoSQL DBMS with the support of
Native Graphs, Documents Full-Text, Reactivity, Geo-Spatial and Object
Oriented concepts. It's written in Java and it's amazingly fast.
